      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and roughly chop your<strong> ginger</strong>, then peel and roughly chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop roughly</p><p>Roughly chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong></p><p>Separate your <strong>coriander leaves </strong>from the <strong>stalks</strong>, then chop them both<strong> </strong>finely</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
