      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped ginger</strong>, <strong>garlic</strong>, <strong>tomatoes</strong>,<strong> chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>coriander stalks</strong> (save the leaves for garnish!) to a <strong>food processor</strong></p><p>Add a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and blitz until smooth – this is your <strong>curry paste</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1715588002477-x200.jpg",
