        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>coconut stock</strong> and cook for 3-5 min or until reduced to a curry-like consistency</p><p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>hake fillet[s]</strong> into large bite-sized pieces</p><p>Once the sauce has thickened, add the <strong>chopped hake</strong> and your <strong>sugar snap peas </strong>to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
