          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for 4-5 min further or until the hake is cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p><p>Remove the pan from the heat and squeeze in the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s] </strong>– this is your<strong> simple hake curry with sugar snap peas</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
