      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>simple hake curry with sugar snap peas </strong>with the<strong> brown rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the<strong> chopped coriander leaves</strong> and a<strong> lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
